name: E-Cell
description:
This is my entry into the Go Godot Jam2.  You play as a ninja bad-@ss who has dropped his energy cells in the weirdest place. Go pick them all up and get to the final scene to see your time. Don't fall off or take too long or you will have to try again (;

W,A,S,D - to move

SPACE - to jump

SHIFT - to run
